aa(lp20
VSP: But is this necessarily a bad thing?
p21
aVPerhaps reason is overrated.
p22
aVMany pundits have argued that a good heart
p23
aVand steadfast moral clarity
p24
aVare superior to triangulations of overeducated policy wonks,
p25
aVlike the best and brightest and that dragged us
p26
aVinto the quagmire of Vietnam.
