aVAnd wasn't it reason that gave us the means
p28
aVto despoil the planet
p29
aVand threaten our species with weapons of mass destruction?
p30
aVIn this way of thinking,  it's character and conscience,
p31
aVnot cold-hearted calculation, that will save us.
p32
aVBesides, a human being is not a brain on a stick.
p33
aVMy fellow psychologists have shown that we're led
p34
aVby our bodies and our emotions
p35
aVand use our puny powers of reason
p36
aVmerely to rationalize our gut feelings after the fact.
